<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="decision-n">decision <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'sɪʒn/    美 /dɪ'sɪʒn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 决定；抉择：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make / take a decision</strong> (= decide) 
作决定</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>arrive at / come to / reach a decision</strong>
作出决定</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Choosing your future career is an extremely important decision.  
选择你将来的职业是一个极为重要的决定。</p><footer>2009 安徽</footer></div>

<h4 id="2u">2.<strong>[U] 果断；坚定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is a man of decision. 
他是一个果断的人。</p></div>

<h4 id="3c">3.<strong>[C] 决议；结论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>pass a decision 
通过一项决议</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>decisive /dɪ'saɪsɪv/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a decisive answer 
明确的答案</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a decisive person 
果断的人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She has <strong>played a decisive role</strong> in the peace negotiations. 
她在和谈中起了决定性作用。</p></div></div>